title: Perle Mediaconverter: Chassis Diagnostic Status
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/perle
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the diagnostic result and alarms of the chassis of
 Perle Mediaconverter devices which support the PERLE-MCR-MGT MIB.

 The check is OK, if all results are passed. It goes WARN if a firmware
 download is required. The check is CRIT if temperature sensor is not
 functional.
 Moreover if the devices reports at least one alarm the check also goes
 CRIT. Otherwise it's OK.

discovery:
 One service is created.
